{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3510", "repo": "rails", "body": "This seems a bit weird to me too, but that's just because it's not the way I'm used to doing things.\r\n\r\nI do think this seems cool though, you don't have to `join` everything all the time. It would be nice to be able to do\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\ncontent_tag :ul do\r\n  @posts.map{|post| content_tag(:li, post.title)}\r\nend\r\n```\r\n\r\nwithout having to explicitly do the `join`.\r\n\r\n+1 from me.", "_id": {"$oid": "52383593bd3543c15100fc5d"}, "issue_id": 3510, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2642775", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3510#issuecomment-2642775", "updated_at": "2011-11-05T22:18:50Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/henrikhodne/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/henrikhodne/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/henrikhodne/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/henrikhodne/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/henrikhodne", "login": "henrikhodne", "gravatar_id": "d036be96167a38393d657c66a25ec85c", "html_url": "https://github.com/henrikhodne", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/henrikhodne/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/henrikhodne/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/henrikhodne/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/d036be96167a38393d657c66a25ec85c?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Ff1ab4591a72bfca2da721ca61a6e9569.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/henrikhodne/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 24421, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/henrikhodne/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2011-11-05T22:18:50Z", "id": 2642775, "owner": "rails"}
